    "steps": [
        "Heat vegetable oil in pan till lightly smoking, turn the heat down to medium.",
        "Add in red bean chilli paste, ginger, garlic, sichuan peppercorns and minced beef and cook for two minutes.",
        "Add sugar, soy sauce, oyster sauce, shaoxing wine, black and white peppers and continue to cook for 3-5 minutes.",
        "Add chicken essence and broth (or water). Mix well and cook at medium low heat for 5 minutes with lid on.",
        "Slowly add cornstarch water around the edge and toss until the meat sauce thickens up.",
        "Mix the meat sauce into cooked noodles and serve with chopping spring onions and cucumber."
